  "title": "Security Officer (15 work days / month)",
  "description": "<p>We are seeking committed and responsible individuals to join our team as In-House Security Officers. As a Security Officer, you will be responsible for ensuring the safety and security of our premises, employees, and visitors. Your primary role will be to patrol designated areas, conduct screenings, and implement law enforcement protocols.</p><p><strong>Benefits of joining ASE Singapore:</strong></p><ul><li>Friendly working environment</li><li>Training provided</li><li>Company transport provided</li><li>Subsidized meals & beverages</li><li>Medical, Dental & Insurance benefits</li><li>Allowances + AWS</li><li>Movie & Birthday vouchers</li><li>In-house gym, massage chairs, recreational games available</li></ul><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Prevent losses and damage by reporting irregularities</li><li>Investigate any incident and accident reports</li><li>Respond to security assistance or emergency from employees and external parties</li><li>Patrol and conduct security inspections at access points</li><li>Manage traffic and direct drivers safely to parking areas</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Must possess valid Security license issued by PLRD</li><li>Able to work on 12-hour day/night shift including weekends and Public Holidays</li><li>Mature and able to work independently</li></ul>",
